## 4. AI Integration

### Google Generative AI (Gemini)
| Aspek | Detail |
|-------|--------|
| **Versi** | `^0.21.0` |
| **Model** | `gemini-2.0-flash-lite` |
| **Fungsi** | Memberikan **rekomendasi mobil Toyota** berdasarkan preferensi pengguna (budget, kategori, kebutuhan, penggunaan, lokasi) |

**Alur kerja AI:**

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Pengguna
    participant Form as Form Rekomendasi
    participant API as /api/ai-mobil
    participant Gemini as Google Gemini AI

    User->>Form: Isi preferensi (budget, kategori, dll.)
    Form->>API: POST request + prompt
    API->>Gemini: chatSession.sendMessage(prompt)
    Gemini-->>API: JSON rekomendasi mobil
    API-->>Form: Parsed response
    Form-->>User: Tampilkan rekomendasi
    Form->>Form: Kirim data ke Google Sheet (logging)
```

**Konfigurasi model:**
- **Temperature**: `0.7` — keseimbangan antara kreatif dan deterministik
- **Response format**: `application/json` — output langsung berupa JSON terstruktur
- **Max tokens**: `8192`

