## 6. Animasi & Transisi

### Motion (Framer Motion) 12
| Aspek | Detail |
|-------|--------|
| **Versi** | `^12.4.5` |
| **Fungsi** | Library animasi deklaratif untuk React — page transitions, hover effects, entrance animations |

Digunakan pada **page transition** (file `template.tsx`):
```tsx
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
  exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95 }}
  transition={{ ease: "easeInOut", duration: 0.3 }}
>
  {children}
</motion.div>
```

